und":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"츠구, 아침부터 계속 일만 해서 안 힘들어?\n모처럼 고등학교로 올라와서 하는 첫 문화제인데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"조금은……\n그래도 즐거운 문화제를 지키는 게 학생회의 일이니까!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"오오, 츠구하네……\n아침에도 일찍 나왔지? 나 같았으면 무리야……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아침에 일찍 모여서 각 반을 체크하고\n사전 미팅도 하고 문화제가 시작되면 학교를 돌면서\n곤경에 처한 반이 있으면 도와주기도 하고……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"역시 조금 피곤하네~…… 냠……\n그러고 보니 란 짱은 메이드 복장이 아니네?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"이, 입을 리가 없잖아!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"A반 녀석한테 들어보니까 강하게 거절한 모양이더라고.\n그 반 녀석들도 란이 메이드복을 입을 걸 기대하고 있던 눈치던데?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"바보 아니야!? 절대 안 입어! 입으면 죽을 거야!\n난 뒤에서 음식을 만드는 역할이니까 안 입어도 된다고!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아쉽다. 메이드복을 입은 란 짱을 보고 싶었는데~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"하핫! 그건 그렇고 고등부 문화제는 역시\n규모가 다르네~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"중등부보다 반도 더 많으니까.\n……그보다도 토모에, 기분이 너무 업됐어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"헤헷! 축제를 좋아하는 피를 그만 주체할 수 없거든~!\n이런 떠들썩한 분위기라면 말이지!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"올해는 손님 수도 작년 대비 1.5배나 되는 것 같아~!\n굉장하지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"1.5배!? 그거 대박아냐?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"설마…… 연극부 효과인가?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아마도 그렇지 않을까?\n치사토 씨 효과가 굉장하네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"시라사기 씨랑 세타 선배가 「로미오와 줄리엣」을 한다고 했던가?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"호오. 그렇다면 사람이 많은 것도 이해가 되네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"세타 선배는 이상한 사람 같지만, 공연 중에는 멋있다나 봐.\n히마리가 흥분하면서 알려줬어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"아하하, 히마리 짱은 세타 선배 팬이었지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"그런 것 같아. 연극부는 앞자리에서 보고 싶어! 라면서\n체육관으로 뛰어갔다고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"그렇구나, 이제 슬슬 체육관에 관객들이 모일 시간이구나……\n난 쉬고 있어도 괜찮은 거려나.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"쉬어도 된다고 한 거 아니야?\n쉴 시간에 쉬지 못하면 큰일난다는 건 츠구미도 잘 알잖아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"우우…… 또 그 소리……\n그치만 역시 좀 걱정되네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"학생회 멤버B","body":"하자와 씨~! 쉬는데 미안해!\n연극부 관객이 체육관에 너무 몰린 것 같아!\n정리 좀 부탁해도 돼?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"그치만 츠구미는 쉬는 중인데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"학생회 멤버B","body":"학생회에게 쉴 틈이란 없어!\n난 쓰레기 수거랑 청소하는 데로 가볼 테니까!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네! 가보겠습니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"학생회 멤버B","body":"고마워! 그럼, 잘 부탁해!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"냠…… 냠, 냠……! 좋아, 오코노미야키 다 먹었다!\n란 짱, 토모에 짱, 잘 먹었어! 그럼 가볼게!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"episode183-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"어어, 어이 츠구! 너무 무리하지는 말라고~ ……이런,\n벌써 안 보이네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"정말…… 또 쓰러지지나 않았으면 좋겠는데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"episode183-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"하지만 저게 「츠구」니까 말이지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode183-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"후훗. ……그러네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"m